{"tid":1025203,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"中國商會擬建設「大阪中華街」　盼成觀光熱點","createTime":"2019-02-17T07:42:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T12:07:29.000Z","uid":221827,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f62973b699b16770a9e98936ec33ef99ac07fe70","tid":1025203,"uid":221827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T07:42:53.000Z","msg":"日本大阪一個由中國商人組成的「大阪華商會」，昨日提倡在大阪市西成區設立「大阪中華街」，爭取開設約100間中式餐館及商店，將西成區發展成觀光據點。不過有附近商戶就擔心會帶來垃圾及噪音問題。<br />\n<br />\n大阪華商會昨日在大阪市內一間中餐館召開會議，並宣布了「大阪中華街」的具體方面。他們希望爭取到2025年大阪關西世博會前，在西成的商店街開設共約100家中餐館、雜貨店、文化設施等，還計劃建設一個中式大門。<br />\n<br />\n包括中國駐大阪總領事李天然在內約200人參加了會議，李天然致辭說，大阪受到全球矚目，只有獲得居民的理解，才能走上繁榮與發展之路，西成能夠成為新景點。商會負責人則認為，如今的西成沒有活力，希望將把它建成眾多人來訪的觀光據點，注入活力。<br />\n<br />\n不過日本共同社引述飛田本通商店街振興協會理事長村井康夫表示，有關計劃是完全出乎意料，擔心會出現垃圾和噪音問題。毗鄰商店街的二手店經營者森雅一則表示，區內很多店舖關閉了，相信新構想會帶來活力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%95%86%E6%9C%83%E6%93%AC%E5%BB%BA%E8%A8%AD-%E5%A4%A7%E9%98%AA%E4%B8%AD%E8%8F%AF%E8%A1%97-%E7%9B%BC%E6%88%90%E8%A7%80%E5%85%89%E7%86%B1%E9%BB%9E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25A8%25AD-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2598%25AA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%258F%25AF%25E8%25A1%2597-%25E7%259B%25BC%25E6%2588%2590%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%2585%2589%25E7%2586%25B1%25E9%25BB%259E%2F&d=MHEGAcVJLkfiWkVsZ9yRxhzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=7ea6959a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25A8%25AD-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2598%25AA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%258F%25AF%25E8%25A1%2597-%25E7%259B%25BC%25E6%2588%2590%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%2585%2589%25E7%2586%25B1%25E9%25BB%259E%2F&h=9ca62e2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%95%86%E6%9C%83%E6%93%AC%E5%BB%BA%E8%A8%AD-%E5%A4%A7%E9%98%AA%E4%B8%AD%E8%8F%AF%E8%A1%97-%E7%9B%BC%E6%88%90%E8%A7%80%E5%85%89%E7%86%B1%E9%BB%9E/</a><br />\n<br />\n蝗蟲又準備佔領多一個據點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e09c2ad2a95c2e9cc4d06aba9bc09ed2fdef90","tid":1025203,"uid":191352,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T07:52:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"011c786ef2c64ef3635f5d7f3774e311a7f6ccc7","tid":1025203,"uid":207462,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T07:54:20.000Z","msg":"西成本身都無咩人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過其實可能係方便廣大中國男人<br />\n俾錢老婆去shopping然後自己走過隔離飛田call G <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係唔知會唔會洗吓太平地先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"787ec515276e22729682a7ef3c8d73d80321e06e","tid":1025203,"uid":11320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T07:55:22.000Z","msg":"又多個藉口比大陸狗去日本失禮人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b271846f6446c31089dbddf05d9a9f9bda62440d","tid":1025203,"uid":128644,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T07:56:14.000Z","msg":"係西成區就好呀 狗咬狗"},{"pid":"165d027f3368018c098f36e0150fe797e2f2e8b4","tid":1025203,"uid":139100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T08:11:29.000Z","msg":"中國領事公然干涉別國內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30da19181d99e37cfec0efbb21b423dbfc6f0bf0","tid":1025203,"uid":82640,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b271846f6446c31089dbddf05d9a9f9bda62440d","tid":1025203,"uid":128644,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T07:56:14.000Z","msg":"係西成區就好呀 狗咬狗"},"citedBy":0,"reply